metadata.name: Ukrainian day
metadata.description:
8 years ago I already heard how the shelling sounds and I hoped never to hear these terrible sounds again, but since 02/24/2022 I hear them every day and in particular while writing this text💔

War turns the whole world, consciousness and values ​​upside down❤️‍🔥

What used to seem important is now a mere trifle.
I want those who look at this picture to appreciate what they have, because you never know at what point everything can change 🙏

I had different dreams but now I only dream of peace❤️🤞
